- Cross-references with Windows Internals Part 1
- Integration section documents relationship with other Windows security skills

**Complements existing skill:**
- windows-internals (Part 1) already exists at security/windows/windows-internals/
- Part 1 covers: processes, threads, memory, I/O, security basics (Chapters 1-7)
- Part 2 covers: advanced system mechanisms, virtualization, management, file systems, boot (Chapters 8-12)

